{"id":231322,"type":1,"name":"小林少年と不逞の怪人","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/5c/e7/231322_l70Ne.jpg","summary":"　　時は大正。帝都を震撼させる大怪盗・怪人二十面相を捕らえようとする少年探偵・小林は、とある謎めいた男と出逢う。仕事もせずに毒舌ばかり吐く高等遊民の彼を疑ううち、小林少年は奇妙な事件へと巻き込まれていく‥‥！\r\n　　江戸川乱歩の名作を華麗に再構築した、人の“闇”を暴き出す大正浪漫ミステリー!! ","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>小林少年与不逞的怪人</li><li><span>册数: </span>5</li><li><span>话数: </span>34</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/7523\">上条明峰</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/128\">講談社</a>、<a href=\"/person/7033\">東立出版社</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/7599\">週刊ヤングマガジン</a></li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/15225\">江戸川乱歩</a></li><li><span>开始: </span>2017-11-27(2017年52号)</li><li><span>结束: </span>2018-10-06(2018年45号)</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":1},"tags":[{"name":"漫画系列","count":1},{"name":"上条明峰","count":1},{"name":"漫画","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":7523,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a3/ac/7523_prsn_5hBQt.jpg","name":"上条明峰","desc":"作者"},{"id":128,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2f/b1/128_prsn_nHh14.jpg","name":"讲谈社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":7033,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/fd/24/7033_prsn_J3N83.jpg","name":"东立出版社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":7599,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/3e/43/7599_prsn_5z4t5.jpg","name":"周刊Young Magazine","desc":"连载杂志"},{"id":15225,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/db/bf/15225_prsn_rTPpB.jpg","name":"江户川乱步","desc":"原作"}],"comic":[{"id":257317,"name":"小林少年と不逞の怪人 (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/84/a9/257317_gsGF8.jpg"},{"id":257318,"name":"小林少年と不逞の怪人 (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/a7/22/257318_206ip.jpg"},{"id":257319,"name":"小林少年と不逞の怪人 (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/c4/10/257319_1J3MO.jpg"},{"id":265637,"name":"小林少年と不逞の怪人 (4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/af/f1/265637_o3eRZ.jpg"},{"id":268026,"name":"小林少年と不逞の怪人 (5)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/35/af/268026_mFK89.jpg"}]}